Package: bayesianICSimulations
Title: Bayesian Interval-Censored Survival Data Simulation and Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alexander", "van Twisk", email = "your.email@domain.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for simulating interval-censored survival data and comparing
    Bayesian inference methods (HMC via Stan, Metropolis-Hastings via JAGS) for
    log-logistic AFT models. Designed for MSc research on MCMC comparison with
    weighted interval-censored data. Includes visualization tools for exploratory
    analysis and standardized analysis pipelines following the ADEMP framework.
